 FEATURES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165220/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.poster.avif?t=1664462105\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165220/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.webm?t=1664462105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165220/extras/71f591bb42e12d8149448055e57317e8.mp4?t=1664462105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedural map generation to make every run just a little different from the last.<br></li><li>15+ Unique item modifiers that alter your gunplay.<br></li><li>50+ Stackable passive upgrade items to infinitely scale your stats.<br></li><li>3 playable breachers with their own playstyle.<br></li><li>8 Varied weapons in your arsenal. </li></ul>",
